{"tid":2231299,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"初學者缺訓練場地","createTime":"2020-10-05T14:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T15:22:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4df2691a65c17cfc09c031395a854a5c303857bd","tid":2231299,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/U67FA7VYQNG2FI3H6OLDN2SWIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FU67FA7VYQNG2FI3H6OLDN2SWIY%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6F0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=3225cd28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FU67FA7VYQNG2FI3H6OLDN2SWIY%2F&h=3dc2c19c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/U67FA7VYQNG2FI3H6OLDN2SWIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n初學者缺訓練場地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p69bng0TmyTHUT5945fKh275Yw8=/3101x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OCURM7QWZRCR3GSA2VV3RDV2AA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp69bng0TmyTHUT5945fKh275Yw8%3D%2F3101x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOCURM7QWZRCR3GSA2VV3RDV2AA.jpg&h=1796210b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFasi<br />\n<br />\nFasi認為現時缺乏統一部門推動單車政策，大部份公園、郊野公園、屋苑都不准單車進入，而坊間對學習單車存有誤解，「咩為之識踩單車？好多人以為識平衡就夠，其實控制到部單車都好緊要，特別呢條新單車徑好多出入路口、上落斜路，如果你唔係好靈活運用煞車技術、轉彎同過馬路知識，都有一定危險&hellip;&hellip;政府解決意外嘅辦法就係唔畀踩、推車，但無做嘢去提升踩單車人士技術」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港聞專題︰斷續不平 大車爭路  天價炒車徑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教練盼推廣踩車文化<br />\n<br />\n自從牛下女車神李慧詩在世界賽上屢獲佳績，單車館落成，加上新單車徑開通，單車運動越來越受歡迎。疫潮下人們work from home，多了時間運動，Fasi成立的「形動單車」公司報班人數也大升八成，奈何疫情下，即使需求殷切，當7月第三波疫潮爆發，政府推出二人限聚令，Fasi無法知道，究竟其公司是否受第599F章限制，界線模糊，故穩陣起見，亦只能開辦私人班，令他們收入大減。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，現時香港缺少適合大人學單車的地方，平時學習就只能到單車徑，但單車徑非常繁忙，不太適合學車，交通安全城則是小朋友限定，將軍澳單車館只是場地單車訓練之用。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"b18697b86bd43599487667ce1879232a64306dc5","tid":2231299,"uid":12302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/004059_c90202eeaec124350e789b4d89f59625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F004059_c90202eeaec124350e789b4d89f59625.jpg&h=77f19f16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d823b1f6bea6073a41345eeb1dda636b2457dcd9","tid":2231299,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"單車好好用 機動性強"},{"pid":"7c873655311cde11307d99ffe2200414ab5457a5","tid":2231299,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d823b1f6bea6073a41345eeb1dda636b2457dcd9","tid":2231299,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"單車好好用 機動性強"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"德國先多人踩呀"}]}